n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d0d0a01c43875c8f22538cdd0e1a9e1229865a7e","tid":2073801,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"英文見到比卡超真係好唔和諧"},{"pid":"a9cb9b57f547e92e2d24e78a7ac248a42c0f95ee","tid":2073801,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5f17ada7062aa7a481f669f0a2063e5804973f0","tid":2073801,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"岩岩發現蘋果日報app有得揀英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以推薦比外國朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQ0ik2U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQ0ik2U.png&h=e524de09&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"得香港先down到<br />\n<br />\n外國down唔到蘋果個app"},{"pid":"dc813084ae9f3425ec41ec5ef09cbd312fed3bb1","tid":2073801,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"幾個笑人old new , 但次次有新聞想問英文source 都無人出聲"}]}